OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774954972
OL,3,CMan charged with the murder of Denis
OL,4,CDonaldson
OL,6,FA man has appeared before a Dublin
OL,7,Fcourt charged with the murder of
OL,8,Fformer Sinn Fein official Denis
OL,9,FDonaldson.
OL,11,FMr Donaldson was shot dead in Co
OL,12,FDonegal in April 2006, months after
OL,13,Fadmitting his role as a police and MI5
OL,14,Fagent over 20 years.
OL,16,FAntoin Duffy, aged in his 40s, of no
OL,17,Ffixed abode, appeared before the non-
OL,18,Fjury Special Criminal Court on Monday
OL,19,Fafternoon charged with the murder of
OL,20,FMr Donaldson at Cloghercor, Doochary
OL,21,Fbetween April 3 and 4 in 2006.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
