PN,44602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774954972
OL,3,CMan charged with the murder of Denis
OL,4,CDonaldson
OL,6,FHe was also charged with the
OL,7,Fpossession of a shotgun and ammunition.
OL,9,FHe was arrested earlier in the day
OL,10,Ffollowing his extradition from
OL,11,FScotland on foot of a European Arrest
OL,12,FWarrant.
OL,14,FDetective Garda Adrian Ahern told the
OL,15,Fcourt that he arrested Duffy at
OL,16,FCasement Aerodrome in Baldonnel on
OL,17,FMonday afternoon.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
