PN,44603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774954972
OL,3,CMan charged with the murder of Denis
OL,4,CDonaldson
OL,6,FHe said he later met Duffy at the
OL,7,FCriminal Courts of Justice in Dublin,
OL,8,Fhanded him a copy of the charge sheet
OL,9,Fand showed him an original copy of the
OL,10,Fcharge sheet.
OL,12,FHe was also charged with the attempted
OL,13,Fmurder of another man in November 2007
OL,14,Fin Co Donegal, and with possession of
OL,15,Fa shotgun and ammunition on the date
OL,16,Fand location in question.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
