PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1774954972
OL,3,CMan charged with the murder of Denis
OL,4,CDonaldson
OL,6,FAppearing before judges James
OL,7,FFaughnan, Patrick McGrath and Sarah
OL,8,FBerkeley, he was remanded in custody
OL,9,Fbefore the next court appearance on
OL,10,FApril 13 where he is to appear in
OL,11,Fperson.
OL,13,FHe was also granted legal aid by the
OL,14,Fcourt.
